snippet.title: NES Longplay [327] Who Framed Roger Rabbit?
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by JagOfTroy

I used to enjoy this game when I was younger but could never get very far.
Now I know why.
The difficulty of the fight with Judge Doom is just way too hard due to the length of it.
You also only have a very small window to destroy him at the end before he one-shots you. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
